name: Altergeist Sylkitas
desc: You can return 1 other "Altergeist" card you control to the hand, then target 1 card your opponent controls (Quick Effect); return it to the hand. If this card is sent from the field to the GY: You can target 1 "Altergeist" Trap in your GY; add it to your hand. You can only use each effect of "Altergeist Sylkitas" once per turn.
